title: 11/03/21 DPS Hour 3 Luke Fickell and Andy Staples
itunes:title: 11/03/21 DPS Hour 3 Luke Fickell and Andy Staples
description:
Cincinnati Bearcats Head Football Coach, Luke Fickell talks to Dan about their number 6 ranking in the first CFP. Coach says that he will leave it up to the talk shows to ask why they are ranked only 6th. Andy Staples talks to Dan about possible Heisman Trophy leaders. Andy says he doesn't think the Heisman will be a QB.
